import { Box, Container, Grid, TextField, Typography } from "@mui/material";
import React from "react";
import theme from "../../../theme/theme";

function Checkout() {
  return (
    <Box sx={{ mt: 2 }}>
      <Container>
        <Grid container spacing={3} row>
          <Grid item xs={12} md={6} lg={8}>
            <Typography
              variant="h6"
              sx={{
                fontWeight: "bold",
              }}
            >
              Billing details
            </Typography>
            <Box
              sx={{
                boxShadow: 3,
                border: `1px solid ${theme.palette.lightgrey.main}`,
              }}
            >
              <Grid container spacing={3} row sx={{p:1}}>
                <Grid item xs={12} md={6} lg={6}>
                  <Typography variant="body1" gutterBottom>First Name:</Typography>
                  <TextField fullWidth label="firstName" name="firstName" size="small" />
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={12} md={6} lg={6}>
                  <Typography variant="body1" gutterBottom>Last Name:</Typography>
                  <TextField fullWidth label="lastName" name="lastName" size="small" />
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={12} md={6} lg={4}>
                  <Typography variant="body1" gutterBottom>Phone:</Typography>
                  <TextField fullWidth label="phone" name="phone" size="small" />
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={12} md={6} lg={4}>
                  <Typography variant="body1" gutterBottom>Email:</Typography>
                  <TextField fullWidth label="email" name="email" size="small" />
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={12} md={6} lg={4}>
                  <Typography variant="body1" gutterBottom>Zipcode:</Typography>
                  <TextField fullWidth label="zipcode" name="zipcode" size="small" />
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={12} md={6} lg={4}>
                  <Typography variant="body1" gutterBottom>Country:</Typography>
                  <TextField fullWidth label="country" name="country" size="small" />
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={12} md={6} lg={4}>
                  <Typography variant="body1" gutterBottom>State:</Typography>
                  <TextField fullWidth label="state" name="state" size="small" />
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={12} md={6} lg={4}>
                  <Typography variant="body1" gutterBottom>City:</Typography>
                  <TextField fullWidth label="city" name="city" size="small" />
                </Grid>
              </Grid>
            </Box>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} md={6} lg={4}></Grid>
        </Grid>
      </Container>
    </Box>
  );
}

export default Checkout;
